A simple API endpoint to update user details
Method: PUT
Request URL: https://reqres.in/api/users/2
Data:
{
	"name": "Sandy Mendoza",
    "job": "Developer",
    "country": "Singapore"

}
Response:
{
    "name": "Sandy Mendoza",
    "job": "Developer",
    "country": "Singapore",
    "updatedAt": "2024-02-21T13:53:30.652Z"
}
